{"tid":1782672,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【靜靜雞】歷來首次不開記者會　公布貧窮報告　去年貧窮 140.6 萬人貧窮十年新高","createTime":"2019-12-14T07:17:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-14T12:51:33.000Z","uid":54337,"like":23,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"c04087dfdf3cd3cb7ab249c7091b8144a3683d5f","tid":1782672,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T07:17:07.000Z","msg":"【靜靜雞】歷來首次不開記者會 公布貧窮報告 去年貧窮 140.6 萬人貧窮十年新高<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%9D%9C%E9%9D%9C%E9%9B%9E-%E6%AD%B7%E4%BE%86%E9%A6%96%E6%AC%A1%E4%B8%8D%E9%96%8B%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E6%9C%83-%E5%85%AC%E5%B8%83%E8%B2%A7%E7%AA%AE%E5%A0%B1%E5%91%8A-%E5%8E%BB%E5%B9%B4%E8%B2%A7%E7%AA%AE-140-6-%E8%90%AC%E4%BA%BA%E8%B2%A7%E7%AA%AE%E5%8D%81%E5%B9%B4%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%98/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%259D%259C%25E9%259D%259C%25E9%259B%259E-%25E6%25AD%25B7%25E4%25BE%2586%25E9%25A6%2596%25E6%25AC%25A1%25E4%25B8%258D%25E9%2596%258B%25E8%25A8%2598%25E8%2580%2585%25E6%259C%2583-%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%25B8%2583%25E8%25B2%25A7%25E7%25AA%25AE%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E5%2591%258A-%25E5%258E%25BB%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%25B2%25A7%25E7%25AA%25AE-140-6-%25E8%2590%25AC%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25B2%25A7%25E7%25AA%25AE%25E5%258D%2581%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%2596%25B0%25E9%25AB%2598%2F&d=wPrcUaBjKD1L%2BB1JqNzGIE2FGjryiJR74P7%2B0uEOyUg%3D&h=968ef114\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%259D%259C%25E9%259D%259C%25E9%259B%259E-%25E6%25AD%25B7%25E4%25BE%2586%25E9%25A6%2596%25E6%25AC%25A1%25E4%25B8%258D%25E9%2596%258B%25E8%25A8%2598%25E8%2580%2585%25E6%259C%2583-%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%25B8%2583%25E8%25B2%25A7%25E7%25AA%25AE%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E5%2591%258A-%25E5%258E%25BB%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%25B2%25A7%25E7%25AA%25AE-140-6-%25E8%2590%25AC%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25B2%25A7%25E7%25AA%25AE%25E5%258D%2581%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%2596%25B0%25E9%25AB%2598%2F&h=29a67ed7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%9D%9C%E9%9D%9C%E9%9B%9E-%E6%AD%B7%E4%BE%86%E9%A6%96%E6%AC%A1%E4%B8%8D%E9%96%8B%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E6%9C%83-%E5%85%AC%E5%B8%83%E8%B2%A7%E7%AA%AE%E5%A0%B1%E5%91%8A-%E5%8E%BB%E5%B9%B4%E8%B2%A7%E7%AA%AE-140-6-%E8%90%AC%E4%BA%BA%E8%B2%A7%E7%AA%AE%E5%8D%81%E5%B9%B4%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%98/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/poor-32_or82h_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fpoor-32_or82h_1200x0.png&h=71728c4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港府今日公布去年貧窮情況，去年貧窮人口達 140.6 萬人，較前年增加 2.9 萬人，貧窮率達 20.4%，創十年以來新高。若計算政府恆常現金政策介入，會令 38.2 萬人脫貧，貧窮率降低 5.5 個百分點。值得留意的是，今次是自 2013 年，政府首次公布《香港貧窮情況報告》以來，首次無召開記者會，只是在政府新聞處公布報告。<br />\n<br />\n《2018 香港貧窮情況報告》指出，本港經濟在去年保持擴張，但增長速度在下半年顯著減慢，人口高齡化、住戶小型化等結構性因素，亦對貧窮數據帶來壓力。政府指，已持續改善不同措施，主要包括提高長者生活津貼，及推展在職家庭津貼。<br />\n<br />\n若按年齡劃分，65 歲及以上長者貧窮人口達 51.7 萬人，貧窮率 44.4%，是各年齡層中最高，政府政策介入後，長者貧窮人口則減少至 36 萬人，貧窮率 30.9%，較前年增加約 2 萬人。政府分析，由於人口高齡化近年明顯加速，長者貧窮率回升，部分原因是綜援及高齡津貼對長者的扶貧成效減弱。政府提到，除現金以外，長者可能更需要非現金援助，例如居家安老、長者醫療等。<br />\n<br />\n18 歲以下兒童貧窮率則為 23.3%，較前年增 0.2 個百分點，但透過政策介入後，兒童貧窮率創有紀錄以來新低，降至 16.8%，下跌 0.7 個百分點，報告認為因有針對性的在職家庭津貼，令扶貧更有成效。"},{"pid":"8e46dd7d249198454d611343d336eaebff978c26","tid":1782672,"uid":62270,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T07:17:47.000Z","msg":"冇時間啦25號截止，極度要人幫手!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1782422\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1782422</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5b9eff49c12444a4a29a02be4231ef48e97bb703","tid":1782672,"uid":126731,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T07:20:34.000Z","msg":"今次反抗咁激，真係唔係無經濟原因。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />堅尼系數大到一個點，都係會爆發。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41400d3e62dc7b545685155587748bde41d4149d","tid":1782672,"uid":10757,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T07