%25E7%25AA%25AE%25E7%258E%2587%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%2596%25BC%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E5%259D%2587%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E5%25B9%25B3-4%25E5%258D%2580%25E6%25AF%258F%25E5%259B%259B%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%2580%258B%25E7%25AA%25AE&d=wPrcUaBjKD1L%2BB1JqNzGIE2FGjryiJR74P7%2B0uEOyUg%3D&h=e48222be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/409860/%E8%B2%A7%E7%AA%AE%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%A3140%E8%90%AC%E5%89%B5%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%98-%E4%B8%83%E5%8D%80%E8%B2%A7%E7%AA%AE%E7%8E%87%E9%AB%98%E6%96%BC%E5%B9%B3%E5%9D%87%E6%B0%B4%E5%B9%B3-4%E5%8D%80%E6%AF%8F%E5%9B%9B%E4%BA%BA%E4%B8%80%E5%80%8B%E7%AA%AE</a><br />\n<br />\n（節略）<br />\n<br />\n政府昨日（13日）發表《2018年香港貧窮情況報告》，被界定為貧窮人口的市民共有140.6萬人創新高；比率為20.4%，僅次於2009的20.6%，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">代表每五名市民，就有一人處於貧窮線以下。</span></span></strong>不過有七區的貧窮率高於整體水平，最差達27%。<br />\n<br />\n18區的貧窮率高低相差近一倍，中西區仍是最低區域，僅14.1%，但按年增加2個百分點，即每七名居民中有一人屬貧窮；最高比率也「冧莊」，觀塘區每四名居民，就有一人處於貧窮狀況，尚有三區的貧窮率都達約24%；全港有五區都有超過10萬人處於貧窮線以下。"},{"pid":"10705c4b0802ee929b99f15d43bef4dacb902d0a","tid":1782672,"uid":14449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5aea15ba112441e75be69a9e130ddde7b7f119a9","tid":1782672,"uid":94982,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"41400d3e62dc7b545685155587748bde41d4149d","tid":1782672,"uid":10757,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T07:21:19.000Z","msg":"條8婆仲做過社署署長 了解基層<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />講春呀"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T07:25:39.000Z","msg":"佢當年做社署最大政績係cut cost<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T07:27:02.000Z","msg":"寫左本署長隨筆<br />\n平時就係j果個"},{"pid":"a9947328e8a572123726af5e73c1dfbda810eb0c","tid":1782672,"uid":91967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T07:28:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00cb8e549777a88e490581319f18